description: Gets data source package information for the behavior graph.

parameters.name: GraphArn
parameters.description: The ARN of the behavior graph.

parameters.name: AccountIds
parameters.description: The list of Amazon Web Services accounts to get data source package information on. (string) ---

nested_items.name: MemberDatasources
nested_items.description: Details on the status of data source packages for members of the behavior graph.

nested_items.name: AccountId
nested_items.description: The account identifier of the Amazon Web Services account.

nested_items.name: GraphArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the organization behavior graph.

nested_items.name: DatasourcePackageIngestHistory
nested_items.description: Details on when a data source package was added to a behavior graph.

nested_items.name: Timestamp
nested_items.description: The data and time when data collection began for a source package. The value is an ISO8601 formatted string. For example, 2021-08-18T16:35:56.284Z.

nested_items.name: UnprocessedAccounts
nested_items.description: Accounts that data source package information could not be retrieved for.

nested_items.name: AccountId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services account identifier of the member account that was not processed.

nested_items.name: Reason
nested_items.description: The reason that the member account request could not be processed.
